Use tomli as TOML parser

The toml library is unmaintained and has known bugs.

Additionally, the tomli library is being integrated into the stdlib in Python 3.11 (PEP 680), making it the best choice of toml library. When we drop support for Python 3.10 and below, we will no longer need tomli as a dependency.
